---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	lang="en"
	title="Contact | Legacy Revival Lab"
	description="Contact Legacy Revival Lab for template-based static product site inquiries."
>
	<section class="page-hero">
		<p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
		<h1>Start with a short email inquiry.</h1>
		<p class="lede">
			Legacy Revival Lab handles product-template based builds. Share what you want to launch,
			which template or product direction fits, and when you want it live.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section aria-labelledby="process-heading">
		<h2 id="process-heading">Inquiry process</h2>
		<ol class="steps">
			<li>
				<strong>Send an inquiry</strong>
				<span>Describe the product, audience, pages, and launch target.</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Confirm requirements</strong>
				<span>Legacy Revival Studio checks the fit and recommends a template-based approach.</span>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Deploy the site</strong>
				<span>Most suitable projects are configured and published through GitHub Pages.</span>
			</li>
		</ol>
	</section>

	<section class="contact-panel" aria-labelledby="email-heading">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">Email-based inquiry</p>
			<h2 id="email-heading">Ready to talk?</h2>
			<p>
				Use email for the first contact. Include a few links or references if they help explain
				the product direction.
			</p>
		</div>
		<a class="button" href="mailto:contact@etern.co.kr">contact@etern.co.kr</a>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.page-hero {
		padding-top: 88px;
	}

	.steps {
		display: grid;
		gap: 12px;
		list-style: none;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.steps li {
		background: #ffffff;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
		border-radius: 8px;
		display: grid;
		gap: 6px;
		padding: 20px;
	}

	.steps span {
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.contact-panel {
		align-items: center;
		background: #ffffff;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
		border-radius: 8px;
		display: flex;
		gap: 24px;
		justify-content: space-between;
		padding: 28px;
	}

	.contact-panel p {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		max-width: 640px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.contact-panel {
			align-items: flex-start;
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
